title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 2)
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 2)
description:
Dawn Viens disappears after her husband David, says the couple has an argument. Police talk with David Viens and Dawn's friends, but are they taking her vanishing act seriously? Some things just don't add up. And then a friend gets a text. Who's Pixie and why is she starting over in another state?
